Compassion must include humility, for it’s the acknowledgement that by creating one who needs compassion, God gave me the gift of being able to bestow compassion.
Express concern to someone with no reward in mind. Do so anonymously in other words.
Today is Nineteen Days, which is Two Weeks and Five Days of the Omer.
Hayom yom chamishi sh’b’shavuah shni la’omer.